
    <title>Health Tips</title>
   
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Health Tips for a Better Life</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center">Good health is a journey, not a destination. Here are practical tips to help you improve your daily habits for better health, wellness, and longevity.</p>

        <section>
            <h2>Exercise Tips</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Stay Active Every Day:</strong> Even a 10-minute walk can make a difference.</li>
                <li><strong>Strength Training:</strong> Build muscle with bodyweight exercises like squats, push-ups, and lunges.</li>
                <li><strong>Stretching:</strong> Prevent injuries and improve flexibility with regular stretching routines.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Nutrition Tips</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Eat Balanced Meals:</strong> Fill half your plate with fruits and vegetables.</li>
                <li><strong>Mindful Eating:</strong> Listen to your hunger cues, avoid overeating.</li>
                <li><strong>Stay Hydrated:</strong> Drink at least 8 glasses of water a day.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Mental Wellness</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Stress Management:</strong> Practice mindfulness and deep breathing exercises.</li>
                <li><strong>Sleep Tips:</strong> Maintain a consistent sleep schedule and avoid screens before bedtime.</li>
                <li><strong>Social Connections:</strong> Spend time with loved ones to maintain emotional health.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

